cell("markdown","# Algorithms 08: Backtracking & Magic Squares\n\n**Learning Objectives:**\n1. Understand how backtracking optimizes brute-force search\n2. Use a `continue` statement to prune hopeless search branches\n3. Solve the $3 \\times 3$ Magic Square computationally\n\n**Prerequisites:** Algorithms 07\n**Estimated time:** 90 minutes\n**Textbook:** *Justin Skycak — Intro to Algorithms & Machine Learning* Chapter 8"),
